d 'SPARKTA': module to produce interactive self-contained HTML charts
d
d   sparkta generates interactive, self-contained HTML charts from
d Stata using a Java backend and Chart.js 4.4. One command produces
d a fully interactive .html file that opens in any browser with no
d server, no Python, and no R required. Supports 20+ chart types
d including bar, line, scatter, CI bars, violin plots, histograms,
d and stacked variants. Features live filter dropdowns, dual-handle
d range sliders, scatter fit lines (7 types) with CI bands,
d reference annotations, collapsible summary statistics panels with
d live updates, and full offline mode. 
d
d KW: charts
d KW: HTML
d
d Requires: Stata version 17
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260320
d
d Author:    Fahad Mirza, NA
d Support: email  fm.109@@hotmail.com
d
f sparkta.ado
f sparkta.sthlp
f sparkta.jar
